<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="icons/icon1.png" type="image/x-icon">

    <title>Help Center</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="help.css">

    <!-- bootstrap css -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- bootstrap Separate -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.10.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-7+zCNj/IqJ95wo16oMtfsKbZ9ccEh31eOz1HGyDuCQ6wgnyJNSYdrPa03rtR1zdB" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-QJHtvGhmr9XOIpI6YVutG+2QOK9T+ZnN4kzFN1RtK3zEFEIsxhlmWl5/YESvpZ13" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.5.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('header.html') %>

<div class="body2" >
    <h2 style="padding-bottom: 50px; padding-top: 50px;">HELP CENTER</h2>
    <div class="container" id="container">
        <div class="form-container ask-container">
            <form action="#">
                <h1>Ask a question</h1>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Question"><br>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email"><br>
                <button style="border-radius: 50px;">Send</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="form-container back-container">
            <form action="#">
                <h2 style="	padding-top: 25px;">Q/A</h2>
                <h5>How should I book s session?</h5>
                <p>To book a session, you must first register or log in if you already have an account. Then click on the "Book a session" button at the end of the page. Then fill out the form.</p><br>
                <h5>Do you have any recommended doctors?</h5>
                <p>Yes, on the main page of our website, if you scroll down the page below, you will find the best specialists in the city of Nur-Sultan.</p><br>
                <h5>Is it possible to make an appointment on your website only in the capital?</h5>
                <p>Yes, at the moment we provide the opportunity to record only in the capital. But we plan to expand in the near future.</p><br>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay-container">
            <div class="overlay">
                <div class="overlay-panel overlay-left">
                    <h1>Welcome Back!</h1><br>
                    <p>Show the most popular questions again</p>
                    <button class="ghost" id="Back" style="border-radius: 50px; ">Back</button>
                </div>
                <div class="overlay-panel overlay-right">
                    <h1>Dear patient!</h1>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>Don't find the answer on your question?</p>
                    <p>Write your question and get an answer</p>
                    <button class="ghost" id="Ask" style="border-radius: 50px;">Ask</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>
    <form action="/" class="back-to-home-container">
        <button style="border-radius: 50px; "> Back to Home </button>
    </form>
    </p>
</footer>
<script src="help.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
